== Events == * {{ill|Daiji|ja|大治|12=draft|12=draft}} 1st year ({{ill|Julian calendar|ja|ユリウス暦|12=draft|12=draft}} [[1126]] {{ill|April 18|ja|4月18日|12=draft|12=draft}}) – The Fudoki ceremony for the gold hall and triple pagoda of 【Chūson-ji|中尊寺】 was held. * {{ill|Bunchi|ja|文治|12=draft|12=draft}} 1st year ({{ill|Julian calendar|ja|ユリウス暦|12=draft|12=draft}} [[1185]] {{ill|April 25|ja|4月25日|12=draft|12=draft}}) – The Battle of Dan-no-ura took place, leading to the extinction of the Taira clan. * [[Ōnin]] 2nd year ({{ill|Julian calendar|ja|ユリウス暦|12=draft|12=draft}} [[1468]] {{ill|April 16|ja|4月16日|12=draft|12=draft}}) – At [[Kata Daiseki|堅田大責]], Enryaku-ji burned the town of Kata in Ōmi Province. * {{ill|Tenmei|ja|天明|12=draft|12=draft}} 4th year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|ja|グレゴリオ暦|12=draft|12=draft}} [[1784]] {{ill|May 13|ja|5月13日|12=draft|12=draft}}) – A young retainer of Tanuma Ittetsu, named Tanuma Itchi, was slain in the palace; he died on the 2nd day of the old month. * {{ill|Kōka|ja|弘化|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} 4th year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|ja|グレゴリオ暦|12=draft|12=draft}} [[1847]] {{ill|May 7|ja|5月7日|12=draft|12=draft}}) – An earthquake struck at Nagano near 【Zenko-ji|善光寺】, with reported casualties of 8,000–12,000.
