ndar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano}} [[1201]] {{ill|April 28|ja|4月28日}}) – {{ill|Chiba Tsunetane|ja|千葉常胤}}, a military commander and governor of Shimōsa (born [[1118]]). * {{ill|Tenpō|ja|天保}} 1st year (leap March) ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦}} [[1830]] {{ill|May 16|ja|5月16日}}) – {{ill|Ishikawa Masamune|ja|石川雅望}}, a Kokugaku scholar (born [[1753]]).
