|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft}} [[1847]] {{ill|May 7|ja|5月7日|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft}}) – An earthquake struck at Nagano near 【Zenko-ji|善光寺】, with reported casualties of 8,000–12,000. == Births ==
== Deaths == * {{ill|Engi|ja|延喜|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft}} 10th year ({{ill|Julian calendar|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|ja|ユリウス暦|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft}} [[910]] {{ill|May 6|ja|5月6日|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft}}) – {{ill|Fujiwara Takako|ja|藤原高子|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft}}, a consort of Emperor Seiwa and mother of Emperor Yōzei (born [[842]]). * {{ill|Bunchi|ja|文治|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft}} 1st year ({{ill|Julian calendar|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|ja|ユリウス暦|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft}} [[1185]] {{ill|April 25|ja|4月25日|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft}}) – Emperor Andoku (【安徳天皇】), the 81st Emperor of Japan (born [[1178]]). * {{ill|Bunchi|ja|文治|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft}} 1st year ({{ill|Julian calendar|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|ja|ユリウス暦|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft}} [[1185]] {{ill|April 25|ja|4月25日|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft}}) – {{ill|Heiji Toki-shi|ja|平時子|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft}}, wife of Taira no Kiyomori and grandmother of Emperor Andoku. * {{ill|Bunchi|ja|文治|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft}} 1st year ({{ill|Julian calendar|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|ja|ユリウス暦|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft}} [[1185]] {{ill|April 25|ja|4月25日|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft}})