== Events == * {{ill|Daiji|ja|大治|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft}} 1st year ({{ill|Julian calendar|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|ja|ユリウス暦|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft}} [[1126]] {{ill|April 18|ja|4月18日|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft}}) – The Fudoki ceremony for the gold hall and triple pagoda of 【Chūson-ji|中尊寺】 was held. * {{ill|Bunchi|ja|文治|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft}} 1st year ({{ill|Julian calendar|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|ja|ユリウス暦|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft}} [[1185]] {{ill|April 25|ja|4月25日|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft}}) – The Battle of Dan-no-ura took place, leading to the extinction of the Taira clan. * [[Ōnin]] 2nd year ({{ill|Julian calendar|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|ja|ユリウス暦|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft}} [[1468]] {{ill|April 16|ja|4月16日|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft}}) – At [[Kata Daiseki|堅田大責]], Enryaku-ji burned the town of Kata in Ōmi Province. * {{ill|Tenmei|ja|天明|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft}} 4th year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft}} [[1784]] {{ill|May 13|ja|5月13日|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft}}) – A young retainer of Tanuma Ittetsu, named Tanuma Itchi, was slain in the palace; he died on the 2nd day of the old month. * {{ill|Kōka|ja|弘化|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft}} 4th year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft}} [[1847]] {{ill|May 7|ja|5月7日|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft}}) – An earthquake struck at Nagano near 【Zenko-ji|善光寺】, with reported casualties of 8,000–12,000. == Births ==
