qq=}}) – {{ill|Heiji Toki-shi|ja|平時子|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Heiji Toki-shi|qq=}}, wife of Taira no Kiyomori and grandmother of Emperor Andoku. * {{ill|Bunchi|ja|文治|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Bunchi|qq=}} 1st year ({{ill|Julian calendar|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|ja|ユリウス暦|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Julian calendar|13=User:Immanuelle/Julian calendar|qq=}} [[1185]] {{ill|April 25|ja|4月25日|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/April 25|qq=}}) – {{ill|Taira no Chimisori|ja|平知盛|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Taira no Chimisori|qq=}}, a military commander and son of Taira no Kiyomori (born [[1152]]). * {{ill|Kennin|ja|建仁|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Kennin|qq=}} 1st year ({{ill|Julian calendar|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|ja|ユリウス暦|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Julian calendar|13=User:Immanuelle/Julian calendar|qq=}} [[1201]] {{ill|April 28|ja|4月28日|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/April 28|qq=}}) – {{ill|Chiba Tsunetane|ja|千葉常胤|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Chiba Tsunetane|qq=}}, a military commander and governor of Shimōsa (born [[1118]]). * {{ill|Tenpō|ja|天保|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Tenpō|qq=}} 1st year (leap March) ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|qq=|qq=draf